title: ESPN videos go dark on YouTube
text:
ESPN videos go dark on YouTube 
Fox News Saturday 24th October, 2015 
YouTube Vice President of Product Management Matthew Glotzbach unveils their new paid subscription service at the YouTube Space LA in Playa Del Rey, Los Angeles, California, United States October 21, 2015. Alphabet Inc's YouTube will launch a $10-a-month subscription option in the United States on October 28 that lets viewers watch videos from across the site without interruption from advertisements, the company said on Wednesday. REUTERS/Lucy Nicholson - RTS5IZU...
